text: Zoë Anina Kressler (born 6 October 2000), known professionally as Zoë Më, is an Swiss singer and songwriter. She represented Switzerland at the Eurovision Song Contest 2025 with the song "Voyage", where she finished 10th with 214 points. ==Discography== ===Studio albums=== Title Details Momoko * Released: 4 September 2020 * Label: Black Paper Boat * Formats: CD, digital download, streaming ===Extended plays=== Title Details Le Loup * Released: 15 March 2024 * Label: Self-released * Formats: Digital download, streaming Dorienne Gris * Released: 17 May 2024 * Label: Self-released * Formats: Digital download, streaming ===Singles=== Title Year Peak chart positions Album SWI AUT ICE LTU SWE Heat.
